{"tid":1473160,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"立場新聞反送中網站 IT應該可以幫到！","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:09:11.000Z","uid":251277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2a5ce161618e8449cf5c520f2c6e8400c869f7","tid":1473160,"uid":251277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:33:39.000Z","msg":"立場新聞反送中網站：<br />\n<a href=\"https://beta.hackfoldr.org/extradition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta.hackfoldr.org%2Fextradition&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=a6d2f856\" target=\"_blank\">https://beta.hackfoldr.org/extradition</a><br />\n<br />\n想俾屋企人清楚咁知道發生咩事 平時一個個post咁send佢哋唔係好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後想自己整個靚靚網站搞個timeline 發現立場一早整咗 不過個timeline14日前已經冇update 個網站都未係好完整 都清楚立場啲資源水深火熱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有冇IT人幫到手 而且個網站好似少人睇 想宣傳下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/我們正架設-反送中-網站/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%9E%B6%E8%A8%AD-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=ec11d4b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%9E%B6%E8%A8%AD-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%2F&h=a5a2c5de\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/我們正架設-反送中-網站/</a> 6月嘅新聞<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我們架設了網站（https://bit.ly/2wOAFA9），當中除了有基本背景資料外，更有一個持續更新的時間軸。此外，也用電腦程式自動統計現有的聯署總數。這樣一方面讓工程師以最擅長的方式參與社運，同時透過自動化減輕了社會運動組織者的工作量，長遠為民主運動累積力量！\n\n如果你也想出一分力的話，歡迎加入公民黑客的行列！請看這個新手介紹（https://bit.ly/2KxAKQO），看看如何參與吧！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n出一分力新手介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1oBobJ7W2fkJMhSXhvdsseYj0AOxSDoQdlGWHR7fg9EU/mobilepresent?slide=id.p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F1oBobJ7W2fkJMhSXhvdsseYj0AOxSDoQdlGWHR7fg9EU%2Fmobilepresent%3Fslide%3Did.p&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=cf888335\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1oBobJ7W2fkJMhSXhvdsseYj0AOxSDoQdlGWHR7fg9EU/mobilepresent?slide=id.p</a><br />\n<br />\n其實想整簡潔又high-tect嗰種 我最多都係去到搞過weebly 入code真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想掟個網站人哋就睇到發生咩事 我都會用下weebly整個 唔想屋企人繼續乜都唔知"},{"pid":"afb341883b793942a69136a8c828ebe456d126ed","tid":1473160,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:36:05.000Z","msg":"芽菜巴好似整緊timeline project<br />\n<br />\n[製作中] 屬於香港人的timeline，團作人員招募<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459590</a>"},{"pid":"74ba262408cab2710d7864f31c9d958b8291c6ad","tid":1473160,"uid":251277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}